This product includes software developed as an independent, community project.

The Royal Enfield Tripper dash link layer (the "K1G" Wi-Fi protocol: RSA-1024 +
AES-256 handshake, H.264/RTP projection, control-plane packet layouts) is an
independent Swift re-implementation whose protocol understanding is cross-checked
against the following open-source projects, all licensed under Apache-2.0:

  - NorthStar    — https://github.com/adityadasika21/NorthStar
  - OpenDash     — https://github.com/subtlesayak/open-dash
  - better-dash  — https://github.com/norbertFeron/better-dash

These are interoperability facts (packet layouts observed on real hardware), not
copied source.

